trange-dontnod-entertainment-grows-up/ |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。已作出的選擇將改變未來，造成短期或長期的影響<ref name="shortlong">{{cite web |url=http://www.polygon.com/2014/10/10/6954961/life-is-strange-story-choices-matter-dontnod |title=Do your choices matter if you can just rewind time and redo them? |first=Samit |last=Sarkar |date=2014-10-10 |publisher=[[Polygon|Polygon]] |accessdate=2014-11-12 |archivedate=2014-11-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141112030805/http://www.polygon.com/2014/10/10/6954961/life-is-strange-story-choices-matter-dontnod |deadurl=no }}</ref>。Dontnod創意總監表示玩家作出的所有選擇均無絕對的對錯之分，短期內有利的選擇或將帶來惡果<ref name="repercussion">{{cite web |url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2014-09-10-life-is-strange-it-takes-time-to-be-different |title=Life is Strange: It takes time to be different |first=Robert |last=Purchese |date=2014-09-12 |publisher=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] |accessdate=2014-11-11 |archivedate=2015-02-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150206232913/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2014-09-10-life-is-strange-it-takes-time-to-be-different |deadurl=no }}</ref>。事件被逆轉後，事先獲得的細節可在未來發揮作用<ref name="reset">{{cite web |url=http://www.gameinformer.com/games/life_is_strange/b/pc/archive/2015/01/23/dontnod-details-the-rules-of-time-manipulation-in-life-is-strange.aspx |title=Life Is Strange Has Strict Time Travel Rules And A Unique Photography Aesthetic |first=Mike |last=Futter |date=2015-01-23 |publisher=[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]] |accessdate=2015-01-24 |archivedate=2015-01-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150127152137/http://www.gameinformer.com/games/life_is_strange/b/pc/archive/2015/01/23/dontnod-details-the-rules-of-time-manipulation-in-life-is-strange.aspx |deadurl=no }}</ref>。時間逆轉前持有的物品能留在主角身上<ref name="inventory">{{cite web |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/gaming/news/a623826/life-is-strange-developer-diary-explores-rewind-feature.html#~p2f4kmNfcbwQbB |title=Life Is Strange developer diary explores rewind feature |first=Liam |last=Martin