==劇情==
2013年10月7日，麦克斯·考非尔德（Maxine Caulfield）<ref name="voicedby1">{{cite web |url=http://gamingbolt.com/life-is-strange-gets-its-final-developer-diary-creating-arcadia-bay |title=Life Is Strange Gets Its Final Developer Diary: Creating Arcadia Bay |first=Martin |last=Toney |date=2015-01-29 |publisher=GamingBolt |accessdate=2015-01-29 |archivedate=2015-02-03 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150203060033/http://gamingbolt.com/life-is-strange-gets-its-final-developer-diary-creating-arcadia-bay |deadurl=no }}</ref>在上艺术课时出現幻視，来到了某个燈塔旁并目擊到巨型[[龍捲風|龍捲風]]摧毁小镇的全过程。惊魂未定的麥克斯下課後来到洗手間却又目睹同学內森（Nathan Prescott）意外槍殺了另一名女生。麥克斯驚呼後發現自己居然回到了剛才的课堂中，于是她迅速在下課後趕到洗手間成功阻止了这起事件，其後發現被救的女生是兒時好友克洛伊（Chloe Price）<ref name="voicedby2">{{cite web |url=http://www.incgamers.com/2015/01/third-life-is-strange-vid-explains-sights-and-sounds |title=Third Life is Strange vid explains sights and sounds |first=Tim |last=McDonald |date=2015-01-29 |publisher=IncGamers |accessdate=2015-01-29 |archivedate=2015-02-03 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150203061730/http://www.incgamers.com/2015/01/third-life-is-strange-vid-explains-sights-and-sounds |deadurl=no }}</ref>。兩人相聚後前往鎮上海岸散步，麥克斯發現岸上燈塔與幻視中所見燈塔相同，隨即再次陷入幻視，发觉災難將於四天後發生。恢复意識後麥克斯向克洛伊透露幻視內容以及其回溯時間的能力<ref>{{cite video game|title=奇妙人生|developer=Dontnod Entertainment|publisher=[[史克威爾艾尼克斯|史克威爾艾尼克斯]]|date=2015-01-30|platform=Microsoft Windows, PlayStation 4, PlayStation 3, Xbox One, Xbox 360|level=Chrysalis}}</ref>。

第二天，麥克斯同學凱特（Kate Marsh）因被拍攝到在一派對中與多名男生發生親暱行為而成為[[網絡欺凌|網絡欺凌]][[受害者|受害者]]，麥克斯與凱特交談後得悉派對由內森主辦，凱特是被药物迷晕而非自願地被拍攝。克洛伊其後邀約麥克斯對其能力進行實驗，麥克斯在多次回溯時間後出现了流鼻血和晕厥的情况。回校後麦克斯发现凱特在一眾學生觀看下准备從女生宿舍楼顶跳下自杀，麥克斯運用能力使時間停頓後到達屋顶進行劝说，此时玩家的對話選擇決定了凱特的命運。事後麥克斯認為这次事件與克洛伊的好朋友、已经失蹤的學生瑞秋（Rachel Amber）有所關係，決定與克洛伊尋求真相<ref>{{cite video game|title=奇妙人生|developer=Dontnod Entertainment|publisher=[[史克威爾艾尼克斯|史克威爾艾尼克斯]]|date=2015-03-24|platform=Microsoft Windows, PlayStation 4, PlayStation 3, Xbox One, Xbox 360|level=Out of Time}}</ref>。當晚二人潛進學園校長辦公室尋找線索，在閱畢校長私人檔案後二人在學園泳池玩樂片刻，遭到警衛追捕的她们最终有惊无险地回到克洛伊家。

第三天，任学校保安队长的克洛伊繼父大卫（David Madsen）歸來後與二人發生口角，麥克斯亦向克洛伊母親透露大衛秘密擁有凱特與瑞秋的檔案。麥克斯认为瑞秋與克洛伊的債主弗兰克（Frank Bowers）關係并不尋常，于是与克洛伊一道潛入弗兰克的房车中進行調查，事实证明瑞秋與弗兰克曾有戀人關係但對克洛伊隱瞞此事。麥克斯回到學園宿舍後細閱一幅她與克洛伊的兒時照片時突然被送回照片拍攝當天——克洛伊生父親威廉（William Price）車禍去世的那天。麥克斯為救威廉而藏起了其車鑰匙使他免於一死，但是此舉让现实进入了另一条时间线：麥克斯與內森及其朋友成了好友、大衛當上了校巴司機、威廉安然無恙、克洛伊却因一次意外车祸而终生瘫痪<ref>{{cite video game|title=奇妙人生|developer=Dontnod Entertainment|publisher=[[史克威爾艾尼克斯|史克威爾艾尼克斯]]|date=2015-05-19|platform=Microsoft Windows, PlayStation 4, PlayStation 3, Xbox One, Xbox 360|level=Chaos Theory}}</ref>。

麥克斯與克洛伊相處一天後決定用那张照片再次返回拍攝當天，撤回當時的決定使時空回復正常。麥克斯與克洛伊利用從大衛、內森和弗兰克處取得的資料繼續進行調查，二人追查至一所由內森家族擁有的廢棄穀倉，發現地下密室內藏有凱特與瑞秋被縛和迷晕的照片，其中一张照片是瑞秋倒在克洛伊常留連的廢料回收場內的土坑內。二人趕往回收場後證實瑞秋已死，愤怒的克洛伊認為內森就是兇手，决定與麥克斯一同前往追捕，二人因其後接獲內森威脅毀滅證據的短訊而折返卻被伏擊，麥克斯被注射了迷藥而克洛伊被射殺，麥克斯在失去意識前看見開槍者是學園攝影老師杰弗遜（Mark Jefferson）<ref>{{cite video game|title=奇妙人生|developer=Dontnod Entertainment|publisher=[[史克威爾艾尼克斯|史克威爾艾尼克斯]]|date=2015-07-28|platform=Microsoft Windows, PlayStation 4, PlayStation 3, Xbox One, Xbox 360|level=Dark Room}}</ref>。

麥克斯被杰弗遜囚禁在地下密室後以現場相片返回第一天的課堂中，向大衛發送短訊告發杰弗遜，事件再次產生新時空：克洛伊生還、杰弗遜被捕、麥克斯勝出一攝影比賽、其得勝相片在[[三番市|三番市]]的相片展覽中展出。麥克斯在展覽場地致電克洛伊，却獲悉阿卡迪亞灣正受預視中的巨型龍捲風吹襲。麦克斯决定利用其展覽相片返回更早的過去以圖再次改變時空，结果發現自身陷入時空的惡夢中，過去的一切縱橫交錯地呈現眼前。麥克斯回復意識後發現自己與克洛伊位於阿卡迪亞灣燈塔旁，这才明白龍捲風就是自己改變時空拯救了克洛伊的后果，面對最後的決擇：返回第一天克洛伊被殺前一刻容許兇案發生以拯救阿卡迪亞灣，或讓龍捲風摧毀阿卡迪亞灣使克洛伊存活。假如麥克斯選擇後者，海灣會被毀滅，麥克斯與克洛伊驅車離開空無一人的廢墟；假如麥克斯選擇前者，克洛伊被內森射殺，內森與杰弗遜被拘捕，麥克斯出席克洛伊葬禮<ref>{{cite video game|title=奇妙人生|developer=Dontnod Entertainment|publisher=[[史克威爾艾尼克斯|史克威爾艾尼克斯]]|date=2015-10-20|platform=Microsoft Windows, PlayStation 4, PlayStation 3, Xbox One, Xbox 360|level=Polarized}}</ref>。

==開發==
遊戲開發於2013年4月展開<ref name="development">{{cite web |url=http://www.incgamers.com/2015/01/life-is-strange-dev-diary-explains-the-story-and-concept |title=Life is Strange dev diary explains the story and concept |first=Paul |last=Younger |date=2015-01-10 |publisher=[[IncGamers|IncGamers]] |accessdate=2015-01-12 |archivedate=2015-01-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150128112720/http://www.incgamers.com/2015/01/life-is-strange-dev-diary-explains-the-story-and-concept |deadurl=no }}</ref>，開發代號為《假如》（What If）。Dontnod Entertainment以出道作《[[記憶駭客|記憶駭客]]》的遊戲機制提出開發概念，繼而創作了主角以配合時間逆轉設定<ref name="birth">{{cite web |url=http://www.xboxachievements.com/news-3925-The-Making-of-Life-is-Strange---An-Indie-Style-Adventure-with-Choice-and-Consequence.html |title=The Making of Life is Strange - An Indie-Style Adventure with Choice and Consequence |first=Richard |last=Walker |date=2015-02-04 |publisher=Xbox Achievements |accessdate=2015-02-07 |archivedate=2015-02-07 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150207161739/http://www.xboxachievements.com/news-3925-The-Making-of-Life-is-Strange---An-Indie-Style-Adventure-with-Choice-and-Consequence.html |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref name="complement">{{cite web|url=http://www.theverge.com/2015/5/19/8612335/life-is-strange-making-of|title=How adventure game Life is Strange blends time travel and teen drama|first=Andrew|last=Webster|date=2015-05-19|publisher=[[The_Verge|The Verge]]|accessdate=2015-05-19|archive-date=2015-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150520104539/http://www.theverge.com/2015/5/19/8612335/life-is-strange-making-of|dead-url=no}}</ref>。工作室基於財務和創作理由決定以章節形式開發遊戲<ref name="format">{{cite web |url=http://www.usgamer.net/articles/life-is-stranges-triforce-of-influences |title=Life is Strange's "Triforce" of Influences |first=Kat |last=Bailey |date=2015-01-31 |publisher=[[USgamer|USgamer]] |accessdate=2015-02-01 |archivedate=2015-02-02 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150202123538/http://www.usgamer.net/articles/life-is-stranges-triforce-of-influences |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，使劇情能以較慢的節奏公開<ref name="slow pace">{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/technology/2015/apr/26/life-is-strange-episodic-video-game-dontnod|title=Life Is Strange: episodic video games prove as addictive as episodic TV|first=Calum|last=Marsh|date=2015-04-26|publisher=[[衛報|衛報]]|accessdate=2015-04-26|archive-date=2016-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160628121659/https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2015/apr/26/life-is-strange-episodic-video-game-dontnod|dead-url=no}}</ref>，亦決定大部分開發資金將用於劇情創作和聘請配音員<ref name="release schedule 1" />。有別於傳統點擊解謎的視覺冒險遊戲，工作室表示《奇妙人生》強調劇情和角色發展<ref name="focus">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamrreview.com/preview/91982/life-is-no-fairy-tale-in-life-is-strange/ |title=Life is no Fairy Tale in Life is Strange - Preview |first=Daniel |last=Carreras |date=2014-09-26 |publisher=gamrreview.com |accessdate=2014-11-11 |archivedate=2014-11-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141112053020/http://www.gamrreview.com/preview/91982/life-is-no-fairy-tale-in-life-is-strange/ |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="intricate">{{cite web |url=http://www.dualshockers.com/2014/08/13/life-is-strange-watch-the-very-first-gameplay-video-and-learn-more-about-dontnods-aaa-indie-game/ |title=Life Is Strange: Watch The Very First Gameplay Video and Learn More About Dontnod’s "AAA Indie" Game |first=Giuseppe |last=Nelva |date=2014-08-13 |publisher=dualshockers.com |accessdate=2014-11-11 |archivedate=2014-11-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141112035701/http://www.dualshockers.com/2014/08/13/life-is-strange-watch-the-very-first-gameplay-video-and-learn-more-about-dontnods-aaa-indie-game/ |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，選擇和後果在劇情發展中扮演重要角色<ref name="choice">{{cite web |url=http://www.polygon.com/2014/8/11/5990851/life-is-strange-dontnod-entertainment-ps4-ps3-xbox-one-360-pc |title=Life is Strange, episodic adventure game, coming from Remember Me dev |first=Samit |last=Sarkar |date=2014-08-11 |publisher=[[Polygon|Polygon]] |accessdate=2014-11-11 |archivedate=2015-02-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150206232452/http://www.polygon.com/2014/8/11/5990851/life-is-strange-dontnod-entertainment-ps4-ps3-xbox-one-360-pc |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

工作室創辦人之一肖恩·莫里斯（Jean-Maxime Moris）談及遊戲背景和藝術風格時表示[[太平洋西北地區|太平洋西北地區]]富有切合遊戲的懷舊和秋天氣氛，有使人探索內心的感覺，因此在早期開發中已被定為劇情發生地點<ref name="setting">{{cite web |url=http://gamerhub.tv/videos/life-is-strange-gameplay-preview-interview/2014/08/27/ |title=Life Is Strange Gameplay Preview Interview |date=2014-08-27 |publisher=gamerhub.tv |accessdate=2014-11-11 |archivedate=2014-11-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141112032016/http://gamerhub.tv/videos/life-is-strange-gameplay-preview-interview/2014/08/27/ |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。團隊到訪當地<ref name="shortlong" />拍攝照片、翻閱當地報章和利用[[Google街景|Google街景]]確保遊戲環境與實境相近<ref name="archetypes">{{cite web|url=http://www.idigitaltimes.com/life-strange-episode-2-dev-talks-us-about-whats-next-max-arcadia-bay-exclusive-424890|title='Life is Strange Episode 2' Dev Talks To Us About What's Next For Max In Arcadia Bay [EXCLUSIVE]|first=Zulai|last=Serrano|date=2015-03-23|publisher=iDigitalTimes.com|accessdate=2015-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150324104026/http://www.idigitaltimes.com/life-strange-episode-2-dev-talks-us-about-whats-next-max-arcadia-bay-exclusive-424890|archive-date=2015-03-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="googlestreetview">{{cite web |url=http://www.vg247.com/2015/01/29/life-is-strange-pc-ps4-xbox-one-video/ |title=Final Life is Strange developer diary focuses on music, voice actors |first=Stephany |last=Nunneley |date=2015-01-29 |publisher=[[VG247|VG247]] |accessdate=2015-01-29 |archivedate=2015-01-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150129233119/http://www.vg247.com/2015/01/29/life-is-strange-pc-ps4-xbox-one-video/ |deadurl=no }}</ref>。為迎合[[現實主義|現實主義]]，劇情內的超自然元素被設定為角色內心掙扎的實體化<ref name="innerconflict">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamereactor.eu/news/288154/Life+is+Strange+-+%22Supernatural+things+merely+metaphors%22/ |title=Life is Strange - "Supernatural things merely metaphors" |first=Bengt |last=Lemne |date=2015-01-26 |publisher=Gamereactor |accessdate=2015-01-26 |archivedate=2015-02-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150206225023/http://www.gamereactor.eu/news/288154/Life%2Bis%2BStrange%2B-%2B%22Supernatural%2Bthings%2Bmerely%2Bmetaphors%22/ |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，遊戲內的材質均為人手著色<ref name="texture">{{cite web |url=http://www.dualshockers.com/2014/08/13/life-is-strange-gets-new-screenshots-showing-dontnods-lovely-art-style-it-looks-super-sweet-on-ps4/ |title=Life Is Strange Gets New Screenshots Showing Dontnod’s Lovely Art Style; It looks Super-Sweet on PS4 |first=Giuseppe |last=Nelva |date=2014-08-13 |publisher=dualshockers.com |accessdate=2014-11-11 |archivedate=2014-11-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141112035246/http://www.dualshockers.com/2014/08/13/life-is-strange-gets-new-screenshots-showing-dontnods-lovely-art-style-it-looks-super-sweet-on-ps4/ |deadurl=no }}</ref>，營造藝術總監稱為「浮光掠影式[[渲染|渲染]]」（impressionistic rendering）的效果<ref name="rendering">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamereactor.eu/previews/249994/Life+is+Strange/|title=One of the oddest reveals of Gamescom also proved to be one of the most interesting. Here's what the Remember Me developers did next.|first=Christian|last=Gaca|date=2014-08-22|publisher=gamereactor.eu|accessdate=2014-11-11|archive-date=2014-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141221190043/http://www.gamereactor.eu/previews/249994/Life%2Bis%2BStrange/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。莫里斯認為現今社會追求原創和變化，團隊不但以創作最佳的遊戲為目標，也提供完全切合玩家要求的體驗<ref name="taste">{{cite web |url=http://metro.co.uk/2014/08/12/square-enix-and-remember-me-creator-announce-life-is-strange-4829195/ |title=Square Enix and Remember Me creator announce Life Is Strange |date=2014-08-12 |publisher=metro.co.uk |accessdate=2014-11-11 |archivedate=2014-11-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141112074739/http://metro.co.uk/2014/08/12/square-enix-and-remember-me-creator-announce-life-is-strange-4829195/ |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

莫里斯表示雖然《奇妙人生》與工作室前一部作品《記憶駭客》有明顯分別，但主題同樣圍繞記憶和身份<ref name="memoryidentity">{{cite web |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/08/13/gamescom-2014-how-life-is-strange-gets-female-protagonists-right |title=Gamescom 2014: How 'Life is Strange' Gets Female Protagonists Right |first=Brian |last=Albert |date=2014-08-13 |publisher=[[IGN|IGN]] |accessdate=2014-11-11 |archivedate=2014-11-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141112052448/http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/08/13/gamescom-2014-how-life-is-strange-gets-female-protagonists-right |deadurl=no }}</ref>，假如《記憶駭客》從[[數位訊號|數位]]角度探討人的身份，《奇妙人生》則從[[類比訊號|類比]]角度審視同一主題<ref name="analogue">{{cite web |url=http://www.crunchyroll.com/anime-feature/2015/01/28/feature-life-is-strange-interview-and-hands-on-impressions |title=FEATURE: "Life is Strange" Interview and Hands-on Impressions |first=Nate |last=Ming |date=2015-01-29 |publisher=Crunchyroll |accessdate=2015-01-29 |archivedate=2015-01-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150129193102/http://www.crunchyroll.com/anime-feature/2015/01/28/feature-life-is-strange-interview-and-hands-on-impressions |deadurl=no }}</ref>。遊戲採用改良的[[魔域幻境引擎|第三代魔域幻境引擎]]製作，以及重用為《記憶駭客》而製作的工具和特別效果<ref name="characters" /><ref name="format" />。[[圖像處理|圖像處理]]、[[多重曝光|多重曝光]]和[[粒子系統|粒子系統]]等視覺效果被用以呈現主角回溯時間時所需的藝術美感<ref name="obstacles">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/watch-life-is-strange-dev-talks-time-travel-butter/1100-6424849/|title=Watch: Life is Strange Dev Talks Time-Travel Butterfly Effect in New Video|first=Eddie|last=Makuch|date=2015-01-23|publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|accessdate=2015-01-24|archive-date=2015-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150125111127/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/watch-life-is-strange-dev-talks-time-travel-butter/1100-6424849/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。遊戲所有章節被指在同一時間製作<ref name="parallel">{{cite web|url=http://www.godisageek.com/2015/01/life-is-strange-interview-with-creative-director-jean-maxime-moris/|title=Life Is Strange: an Interview with Creative Director Jean-Maxime Moris|first=Mike|last=Stubbsy|date=2015-01-26|publisher=God is a Geek|accessdate=2015-01-26|archive-date=2015-01-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150130031705/http://www.godisageek.com/2015/01/life-is-strange-interview-with-creative-director-jean-maxime-moris/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，使開發團隊能根據玩家反應進行調整<ref name="birth" />。團隊參考的其他作品包括《[[行屍_(遊戲)|行屍]]》、《{{link-en|歸家|Gone Home}}》、《[[暴雨殺機|暴雨殺機]]》<ref name="analogue" /><ref name="influences">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamerevolution.com/manifesto/juno--donnie-darko--gone-home--life-is-strange-30843#/slide/8 |title=Juno + Donnie Darko + Gone Home = Life is Strange |first=Blake |last=Peterson |date=2015-01-26 |publisher=[[Game_Revolution|Game Revolution]] |accessdate=2015-01-29 |archivedate=2015-01-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150129222908/http://www.gamerevolution.com/manifesto/juno--donnie-darko--gone-home--life-is-strange-30843#/slide/8 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>、以及《[[麥田捕手|麥田捕手]]》<ref name="catcher">{{cite web |url=http://www.siliconera.com/2015/02/05/life-strange-director-talks-theme-identity-visual-novels/ |title=Life Is Strange Director Talks About The Theme Of "Identity" And Visual Novels |date=2015-02-05 |publisher=Siliconera |accessdate=2015-02-06 |archivedate=2015-02-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150210122205/http://www.siliconera.com/2015/02/05/life-strange-director-talks-theme-identity-visual-novels/ |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。為協助玩家理解遊戲角色，團隊先以[[原型|原型]]人物設定角色，其後才加以改變<ref name="archetypes"/>。

遊戲是Dontnod Entertainment第二部以女性為主角的作品，開發日記提及<ref name="first">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/publishers-said-you-cant-have-a-female-character-says-remember-me-dev/1100-6405550/ |title=Publishers said 'You can't have a female character,' says Remember Me dev |first=Eddie |last=Makuch |date=2013-03-19 |publisher=gamespot.com |accessdate=2014-11-12 |archivedate=2013-12-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131229210302/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/publishers-said-you-cant-have-a-female-character-says-remember-me-dev/1100-6405550/ |deadurl=no }}</ref>工作室曾被其他潛在發行商要求使用男性主角<ref name="square1">{{cite web |url=http://www.playstationlifestyle.net/2015/01/11/life-is-strange-game-dev-diary/ |title=Publishers Wanted a Male Lead Character in Life is Strange, Says Dontnod |first=Zarmena |last=Khan |date=2015-01-11 |publisher=PlayStation LifeStyle |accessdate=2015-01-12 |archivedate=2015-02-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150206165810/http://www.playstationlifestyle.net/2015/01/11/life-is-strange-game-dev-diary/ |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="square2">{{cite web |url=http://www.escapistmagazine.com/news/view/139401-Publishers-Disliked-Dontnods-Life-is-Strange-Having-Female-Leads |title=Publishers Wanted Life is Strange Devs to Make Leads Male |first=Sarah |last=LeBoeuf |date=2015-01-11 |publisher={{link-en|The Escapist|The Escapist}} |accessdate=2015-01-12 |archivedate=2015-02-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150206164909/http://www.escapistmagazine.com/news/view/139401-Publishers-Disliked-Dontnods-Life-is-Strange-Having-Female-Leads |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。莫里斯以[[玩家門|玩家門]]事件為例指出此事值得討論<ref name="50%" />，但強調工作室無意以該事件吸引目光，而是希望創作理想的遊戲和採用切合劇情的角色，因而使用兩名女性主角<ref name="characters"/>。遊戲總監對此表示主角性別對創作良好的劇情而言關係不大<ref name="AMA">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/main-character-s-gender-irrelevant-to-creating-a-g/1100-6425024/|title=Main Character's Gender Irrelevant to Creating a Good Story, Life is Strange Dev Says|first=Emanuel|last=Maiberg|date=2015-02-01|publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|accessdate=2015-02-01|archive-date=2015-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150204063146/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/main-character-s-gender-irrelevant-to-creating-a-g/1100-6425024/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

遊戲音樂由樂團{{link-en|Syd Matters|Syd Matters}}成員強納森·莫萊里（Jonathan Morali）創作<ref name="morali">{{cite web |url=http://connecteddigitalworld.com/2015/01/29/final-dev-diary-for-life-is-strange-announces-soundtrack/ |title=Final Dev Diary for Life is Strange announces soundtrack |first=Chris |last=Hare |date=2015-01-29 |publisher=Connected Digital World |accessdate=2015-01-29 |archivedate=2015-01-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150130043359/http://connecteddigitalworld.com/2015/01/29/final-dev-diary-for-life-is-strange-announces-soundtrack/ |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。樂曲參考了現代{{link-en|獨立民謠|indie folk}}<ref name="folk">{{cite web |url=http://culturefly.co.uk/dontnod-entertainment-reveals-more-about-the-strange-goings-on-in-life-is-strange/ |title=Dontnod Entertainment Reveals More About the Strange Goings On In Life Is Strange |first=Jack |last=Skinner |date=2014-09-28 |publisher=culturefly.co.uk |accessdate=2014-11-11 |archivedate=2014-12-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141209152354/http://culturefly.co.uk/dontnod-entertainment-reveals-more-about-the-strange-goings-on-in-life-is-strange/ |deadurl=no }}</ref>，以營造遊戲氣氛和「穿透一切劇情、藝術和聲音層面」為提而創作<ref name="repercussion" />，融合版權音樂與原創音樂<ref name="50%">{{cite web |url=http://www.dualshockers.com/2014/10/09/life-is-strange-creative-director-jean-maxime-moris-talks-atmosphere-choices-and-female-leads/ |title=Life Is Strange Creative Director Jean-Maxime Moris Talks Atmosphere, Choices, and Female Leads |first=Joel |last=Taveras |date=2014-10-09 |publisher=dualshockers.com |accessdate=2014-11-11 |archivedate=2014-11-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141112040959/http://www.dualshockers.com/2014/10/09/life-is-strange-creative-director-jean-maxime-moris-talks-atmosphere-choices-and-female-leads/ |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="blend">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamerheadlines.com/2015/01/dontnod-entertainment-reveals-life-stranges-third-final-developer-diary/ |title=Dontnod Entertainment Reveals Life Is Strange’s Third and Final Developer Diary |first=Adnan |last=Riaz |date=2015-01-29 |publisher=Gamer Headlines |accessdate=2015-01-29 |archivedate=2015-01-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150130043647/http://www.gamerheadlines.com/2015/01/dontnod-entertainment-reveals-life-stranges-third-final-developer-diary/ |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，版權音樂來自多位作曲者<ref name="artists">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/these-are-the-songs-in-life-is-strange/1100-6425751/|title=These Are the Songs in Life is Strange|first=Alexa Ray|last=Corriea|date=2015-03-07|publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|accessdate=2015-03-07|archive-date=2015-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150309211114/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/these-are-the-songs-in-life-is-strange/1100-6425751/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[Feral_Interactive|Feral Interactive]]稍候將本遊戲[[移植_(軟體)|移植]]到了[[macOS|OS X]]和[[Linux|Linux]]平台，分別在2016年6月16日和7月21日發行。<ref name="mac">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/pressreleases/275134/Life_is_Strange_ndash_out_now_on_the_Mac_App_Store_Thecritically_acclaimed_Life_is_Strangetrade_is_now_available_on_theMac_App_Store_Life_is_Strange_is_a_unique_fivepart_adventure_thatexplores_complex_issues_with_an_innovative_take_on_storybased.php|title=Life is Strange – out now on the Mac App Store The critically acclaimed Life is Strange™ is now available on the Mac App Store! Life is Strange is a unique five-part adventure that explores complex issues with an innovative take on story-based|date=2016-06-16|publisher=''[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]]''|accessdate=2016-06-16|archive-date=2016-09-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160922213029/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/pressreleases/275134/Life_is_Strange_ndash_out_now_on_the_Mac_App_Store_Thecritically_acclaimed_Life_is_Strangetrade_is_now_available_on_theMac_App_Store_Life_is_Strange_is_a_unique_fivepart_adventure_thatexplores_complex_issues_with_an_innovative_take_on_storybased.php|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="porting">{{cite web|url=http://www.hardcoregamer.com/2016/06/01/feral-interactive-confirms-life-is-strange-is-coming-to-mac-linux/209664/|title=Feral Interactive Confirms Life Is Strange is Coming to Mac, Linux|first=Adnan|last=Riaz|date=2016-06-01|publisher=''[[Hardcore_Gamer|Hardcore Gamer]]''|accessdate=2016-06-02|archive-date=2016-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160602111105/http://www.hardcoregamer.com/2016/06/01/feral-interactive-confirms-life-is-strange-is-coming-to-mac-linux/209664/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="linux">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/pressreleases/277641/Life_Is_Strange_is_out_now_on_Steam_for_Mac_and_Linux_withthe_first_episode_available_for_free.php|title=Life Is Strange is out now on Steam for Mac and Linux, with the first episode available for free!|date=2016-07-21|publisher=''[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]]''|accessdate=2016-07-22|archive-date=2016-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160725161020/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/pressreleases/277641/Life_Is_Strange_is_out_now_on_Steam_for_Mac_and_Linux_withthe_first_episode_available_for_free.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===發行===
[[史克威爾艾尼克斯|史克威爾艾尼克斯]]與Dontnod Entertainment於2014年8月11日公開遊戲<ref name="direct">{{cite web |url=http://eu.square-enix.com/en/blog/announcing-life-strange |title=Announcing Life is Strange! |first=Toby |last=Palm |date=2014-08-11 |publisher=square-enix.com |accessdate=2014-12-10 |archivedate=2014-10-21 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141021194250/http://eu.square-enix.com/en/blog/announcing-life-strange |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="announcement">{{cite web |url=http://www.dualshockers.com/2014/08/11/life-is-strange-announced-by-square-enix-for-ps4-xbox-one-ps3-xbox-360-and-pc-first-screenshots/ |title=Life Is Strange Announced by Square Enix for PS4, Xbox One, PS3, Xbox 360 and PC; First Screenshots Released |first=Giuseppe |last=Nelva |date=2014-08-11 |publisher=dualshockers.com |accessdate=2014-11-11 |archivedate=2014-11-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141112035327/http://www.dualshockers.com/2014/08/11/life-is-strange-announced-by-square-enix-for-ps4-xbox-one-ps3-xbox-360-and-pc-first-screenshots/ |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。2014年11月，發行商表示有興趣以光碟版發行遊戲<ref name="physical">{{cite web |url=http://www.videogamer.com/ps4/life_is_strange/news/square_enix_considering_boxed_release_for_life_is_strange.html |title=Square Enix considering boxed release for Life is Strange |first=David |last=Scammell |date=2014-11-19 |publisher=videogamer.com |accessdate=2014-12-06 |archivedate=2014-12-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141208080118/http://www.videogamer.com/ps4/life_is_strange/news/square_enix_considering_boxed_release_for_life_is_strange.html |deadurl=no }}</ref>，但他們當時全力處理[[數位發行|數位發行]]版本<ref name="per cent">{{cite web |url=http://gamingbolt.com/square-enix-considering-retail-release-for-life-is-strange |title=Square Enix Considering Retail Release for Life is Strange |first=Pramath |last=Parijat |date=2014-11-20 |publisher=gamingbolt.com |accessdate=2014-12-06 |archivedate=2014-12-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141210135637/http://gamingbolt.com/square-enix-considering-retail-release-for-life-is-strange |deadurl=no }}</ref>。第一章發行日期於9月時公佈為2015年1月30日<ref name="30Jan2015">{{cite web |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/12/17/life-is-strange-gets-a-release-date-and-pricing-info |title=Life is Strange Gets a Release Date and Pricing Info |first=Wesley |last=Copeland |date=2014-12-17 |publisher=ign.com |accessdate=2014-12-17 |archivedate=2015-02-17 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150217003020/http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/12/17/life-is-strange-gets-a-release-date-and-pricing-info |deadurl=no }}</ref>，同時公開遊戲首部宣傳片段<ref name="reveal">{{cite web |url=http://www.joystiq.com/2014/12/17/time-bending-teen-drama-life-is-strange-debuts-next-month/ |title=Time-bending teen drama Life is Strange debuts next month |first=Sinan |last=Kubba |date=2014-12-17 |publisher=joystiq.com |accessdate=2014-12-17 |archivedate=2015-02-14 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150214185712/http://www.joystiq.com/2014/12/17/time-bending-teen-drama-life-is-strange-debuts-next-month/ |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

2015年2月，第二章的未完成版本流入互聯網<ref name="unfinished">{{cite web |url=http://apgnation.com/articles/2015/02/06/14020/life-strange-episode-2-leaked |title=Life is Strange Episode 2 Leaked |first=Nick |last=Bayer |date=2015-02-06 |publisher=APGNation |accessdate=2015-02-09 |archivedate=2015-02-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150209133836/http://apgnation.com/articles/2015/02/06/14020/life-strange-episode-2-leaked |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="leak">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamerheadlines.com/2015/02/future-unpolished-episodes-life-strange-leaked/ |title=Future Unpolished Episodes of Life is Strange leaked! |first=Jalane |last=Farrington |date=2015-02-06 |publisher=Gamer Headlines |accessdate=2015-02-09 |archivedate=2015-02-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150209133801/http://www.gamerheadlines.com/2015/02/future-unpolished-episodes-life-strange-leaked/ |deadurl=yes |df= }}</ref>，Dontnod的代表作出回應，對他們花了許多時間和心血製作的東西以未完成的狀態對外公開感到難過，呼籲玩家不要下載，以及保證遊戲完成版本將更完善和將在3月中發行<ref name="inresponse">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamereactor.eu/news/289814/Second+episode+of+Life+is+Strange+has+leaked/|title=Second episode of Life is Strange has leaked|first=Jonas|last=Mäki|date=2015-02-09|publisher=Gamereactor|accessdate=2015-02-09|archive-date=2015-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150209141346/http://www.gamereactor.eu/news/289814/Second+episode+of+Life+is+Strange+has+leaked/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2月26日，電子遊戲網誌[[Destructoid|Destructoid]]宣佈第二章將延期發行，無法趕及預定發行日3月13日<ref name="destructoid">{{cite web |url=http://www.destructoid.com/square-enix-life-is-strange-episode-2-delayed-288310.phtml |title=Life is Strange Episode 2 launch has been delayed |first=Kyle |last=MacGregor |date=2015-02-26 |publisher=[[Destructoid|Destructoid]] |accessdate=2015-03-05 |archivedate=2015-02-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150228044324/http://www.destructoid.com/square-enix-life-is-strange-episode-2-delayed-288310.phtml |deadurl=no }}</ref>，但澄清仍將於3月底前推出<ref name="clarified">{{cite web|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2015-02-27-life-is-strange-dev-promises-second-episode-in-march|title=Life is Strange dev promises second episode in March|first=Tom|last=Phillips|date=2015-02-27|publisher=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]|accessdate=2015-03-05|archive-date=2015-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150301202608/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2015-02-27-life-is-strange-dev-promises-second-episode-in-march|dead-url=no}}</ref>。第二章於3月中製作完成<ref name="finished">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamezone.com/news/life-is-strange-episode-2-submitted-for-certification-but-no-release-date-yet-3414046|title=Life Is Strange Episode 2 submitted for certification, but no release date yet|first=Matt|last=Liebl|date=2015-03-07|publisher=[[GameZone|GameZone]]|accessdate=2015-03-08|archive-date=2015-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150308045046/http://www.gamezone.com/news/life-is-strange-episode-2-submitted-for-certification-but-no-release-date-yet-3414046|dead-url=no}}</ref>，發行日期定為3月24日<ref name="Rezzed">{{cite web |url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2015-03-14-life-is-strange-episode-2-release-date |title=Life is Strange: Episode 2 release date revealed |first=Tom |last=Phillips |date=2015-03-14 |publisher=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] |accessdate=2015-03-14 |archivedate=2015-03-15 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150315053810/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2015-03-14-life-is-strange-episode-2-release-date |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

Dontnod在與英國電子遊戲網站[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]的會談中否認有報告指六星期一章節之發行週期是造成延期的原因<ref name="release schedule 1">{{cite web |url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2015-03-18-publishers-wanted-life-is-stranges-main-character-to-be-a-guy-qtes-added |title=Life is Strange dev talks lip-syncing, release schedule and publisher demands |first=Tom |last=Phillips |date=2015-03-18 |publisher=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] |accessdate=2015-03-18 |archivedate=2015-03-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150318133732/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2015-03-18-publishers-wanted-life-is-stranges-main-character-to-be-a-guy-qtes-added |deadurl=no }}</ref>，遊戲總監表示他們正盡全力，目標週期是兩個月之內<ref name="release schedule 2">{{cite web|url=http://www.videogamer.com/ps4/life_is_strange/news/life_is_strange_episodes_wont_release_more_than_two_months_apart.html|title=Life is Strange episodes won't release more than two months apart|first=James|last=Orry|date=2015-03-18|publisher=VideoGamer.com|accessdate=2015-03-18|archive-date=2015-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150705192041/http://www.videogamer.com/ps4/life_is_strange/news/life_is_strange_episodes_wont_release_more_than_two_months_apart.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。第三章其後在5月19日發行<ref name="19 May 2015">{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2015/05/13/life-is-strange-episode-3-chaos-theory-gets-a-release-date|title=Life is Strange: Episode 3 - Chaos Theory Gets a Release Date|first=Luke|last=Karmali|date=2015-05-13|publisher=[[IGN|IGN]]|accessdate=2015-05-13|archive-date=2018-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180622083737/http://www.ign.com/articles/2015/05/13/life-is-strange-episode-3-chaos-theory-gets-a-release-date|dead-url=no}}</ref>；被指規模比前三章均要大的第四章<ref name="ambitious">{{cite web|url=http://www.hardcoregamer.com/2015/07/15/dontnod-entertainment-applying-final-touches-to-life-is-strange-episode-4-dark-room/158734/|script-title=en:Dontnod Entertainment ‘Applying Final Touches’ to Life Is Strange Episode 4: Dark Room|first=Adrian|last=Riaz|date=2015-07-15|publisher=Hardcore Gamer|accessdate=2015-07-23|archivedate=2015-07-22|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150722003041/http://www.hardcoregamer.com/2015/07/15/dontnod-entertainment-applying-final-touches-to-life-is-strange-episode-4-dark-room/158734/|deadurl=no}}</ref>在7月28日發行<ref name="28 July 2015">{{cite web|url=http://www.vg247.com/2015/07/23/life-is-strange-episode-4-release-date-announced-as-sales-hit-one-million-copies/|title=Life is Strange episode 4 release date announced as sales hit one million copies|first=Shabana|last=Arif|date=2015-07-23|publisher=VG247|accessdate=2015-07-23|archive-date=2015-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150723224952/http://www.vg247.com/2015/07/23/life-is-strange-episode-4-release-date-announced-as-sales-hit-one-million-copies/|dead-url=no}}</ref>；最後一章於10月20日發行<ref name="20 October 2015">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/life-is-stranges-final-episode-release-date-announ/1100-6430765/|title=Life is Strange's Final Episode Release Date Announced|first=Eddie|last=Makuch|date=2015-09-21|publisher=''GameSpot''|accessdate=2015-09-22|archive-date=2015-09-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150922235918/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/life-is-stranges-final-episode-release-date-announ/1100-6430765/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

遊戲將有日本語版本，對應微軟視窗、PlayStation 4與PlayStation 3<ref name="japanese">{{cite web|url=http://www.hardcoregamer.com/2015/09/08/square-enix-releasing-life-is-strange-in-japan/166226/|title=Square Enix Releasing Life Is Strange in Japan|first=Adnan|last=Riaz|date=2015-09-08|publisher=''Hardcore Gamer''|accessdate=2015-09-08|archive-date=2015-09-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150910031932/http://www.hardcoregamer.com/2015/09/08/square-enix-releasing-life-is-strange-in-japan/166226/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。實體零售版本被定於2016年1月19日發行，對應PlayStation 4與Xbox One，歐洲區內則於2016年1月22日發行。限定版將有畫冊、原聲大碟、樂譜與總監評論<ref name="NAEU">{{cite web|url=http://www.hardcoregamer.com/2015/11/12/life-is-strange-limited-edition-announced/176838/|title=Life is Strange Limited Edition Announced|first=Adam|last=Beck|date=2015-11-12|publisher=''Hardcore Gamer''|accessdate=2015-11-12|archive-date=2015-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151115010710/http://www.hardcoregamer.com/2015/11/12/life-is-strange-limited-edition-announced/176838/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="EU">{{cite web|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2015-11-12-life-is-strange-to-receive-a-limited-edition-retail-release|title=Life is Strange is getting a Limited Edition retail release|first=Jeffrey|last=Matulef|date=2015-11-12|publisher=''Eurogamer''|accessdate=2015-11-12|archive-date=2015-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151113014002/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2015-11-12-life-is-strange-to-receive-a-limited-edition-retail-release|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

